{"tid":239600,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你覺得每一日都唔開心","createTime":"2017-05-11T19:02:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T15:07:51.000Z","uid":58757,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08fd153f00b975f812fb8afb40caf26060d43796","tid":239600,"uid":58757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T19:02:20.000Z","msg":"你可能冇方向<br />\n你可能失去希望<br />\n你或者因爲香港呢個咁大壓力嘅地方覺得好難生存<br />\n你屋企人未必明<br />\n朋友唔方便成日打擾<br />\n不過你仲有機會睇到呢個post<br />\n可以感受到夏天嘅來臨<br />\n可以聽音樂<br />\n可以因爲別人嘅故事而受感動<br />\n可以體會人生甜酸苦辣<br />\n見證人世間溫暖<br />\n能夠生存本身就係一個blessing(幸運?)<br />\n你可能而家呢刻睇唔到出路<br />\n不過希望你抱住繼續走落去嘅信念<br />\nOne day at a time<br />\n慢慢變成心目中嘅自己<br />\n變得更強大 自信 <br />\n令身邊嘅人覺得認識你係一件幸福嘅事<br />\n做一個努力、善良嘅人，就吸引幸運嘅事發生<br />\n耕種什麼就會收穫什麼<br />\n加油！支持你！"},{"pid":"d86c31892361aad112879ab296f370bed1b770f3","tid":239600,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T19:03:44.000Z","msg":"我想食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f7967217942bbbb52b017834eaa542fd0bd8f5e","tid":239600,"uid":58757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T19:05:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想食宵夜 不過話左要戒"},{"pid":"268d09314c82eb14403ead74185faae4ab246a91","tid":239600,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T19:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想食宵夜 不過話左要戒</blockquote><br />\n無得食野會好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6b9c96009225f9f948a34edb64182dc25618a4","tid":239600,"uid":74088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T19:15:32.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打 睇到最後有啲眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望下個鐘又三點 出面啲雀都醒哂 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{