野成功又冇目標 真係快撚d死左佢唔好阻住人</blockquote><br />\n試下日行一善<br />\n好娘但會令到自己好開心<br />\n可以係好小事 唔一定要係幫人<br />\n個目的係令一個人開心<br />\n我有時會好on9咁random讚下身邊嘅人著衫好睇<br />\n讚下服務性行業嘅呀哥呀姐好專業<br />\n見到人地開心笑自己就好有動力<br />\n我自己長遠目標都係好膚淺 上樓結婚生仔<br />\n但我嘅終身目標係希望做一個善良嘅人，每日都開開心心，令身邊嘅人都被我感染。"},{"pid":"1f70a5bad7eac93821a73bbf9d51e267cf4bdde8","tid":239600,"uid":58757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T19:32:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生，容易<br />\n活，容易<br />\n生活，不容易<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講得啱 生活係艱難 但生命亦都好美好呀"},{"pid":"a91849d17d51470df1506ed3a54e284c80b2ef71","tid":239600,"uid":58757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T19:32:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>多謝巴打 睇到最後有啲眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望下個鐘又三點 出面啲雀都醒哂 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都瞓唔著呀<br />\n聽日又靠咖啡頂硬上</blockquote><br />\n星期五值唔值得開心？定係會更忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我聽日考試。。 有排都未考完"},{"pid":"7feea30dbf56beaff830170ab619b7d6556aadbe","tid":239600,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T19:32:53.000Z","msg":"你拼命過生活 我hea住去生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ac2f681366cef2db4dc6fef661448b4b726890","tid":239600,"uid":14601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T19:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044ff44a5c5feb0486e3d6df9a9f0ad3c1ed8655","tid":239600,"uid":58757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T19:36:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你拼命過生活 我hea住去生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果hea下hea下又一天<br />\n你對生活感到富足 滿意 咁樣冇問題呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果你仲有追